gative (this study; J.</s><s>Bowman, personal communication).</s><s>Filamentous or helical cells may occur in some species.</s><s>Some species grow between 4 and 40 °C: optimal growth occurs at approximately 25 °C.</s><s>The major fatty acids are anteiso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub> and iso-C<sub>15 : 0</sub>.</s><s>The DNA G+C contents are in the range 33.5–39.1 mol%.</s></p></content></protolog>